video.title: Millennials
video.synopsis: A group of millennials copes with the pressures of adulthood by tackling a diverse set of problems from unemployment to cheating.

episodes.synopsis: Benja, a directionless millennial, meets Juanma, who is developing a new app. Benja aims to strike up a partnership with Juanma.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Benja hooks up with Juanma's girlfriend, Flor. Encouraged by his therapist, Rodri confronts Alma and suggests that they break up.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Ariana tells Benja that she has little time left. Benja and Juanma each try to sell the app on their own. Flor is pregnant but doesn't know by whom.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Alma uses Flor's pregnancy test to pretend that she is expecting Rodri's baby. Juanma learns that Flor cheated on him with Benja and plots revenge.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Ariana receives a video of Benja having a threesome. Benja and Juanma discover that an app named "Comoencasa" already exists.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Ariana surprises Benja with a racy suggestion. Flor decides to kick Juanma out, then gets involved with Brian, a mason. Juanma has sex with Alma.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Ariana want to have a threesome with Gaby. Alma and Juanma deal with guilt and consequences from deceiving Rodri.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Ariana discover that Gaby stole money from them. Brian flees after being accused of theft. Juanma gets close to Flor again.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Ariana, Flor, and Alma decide to make their own app. The secrets and betrayals in the group come to light. Alma is in a tricky situation.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Benja has a passionate encounter with Fabi, not knowing that she's Facu's alter ego. The girls' app is a success. Lucas charms everyone at the office.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Benja discovers Facu's double identity. While Ariana avoids Lucas, Flor goes all out to dazzle him. Juanma and Rodri practice their seduction skills.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Ariana hides how sick she really is. Juanma and Rodri throw a party that gets out of hand, exposing everyone's true motivations and personalities.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Benja learns how sick Ariana really is. Octavio is hounded by creditors. Alma offers Rodri help in exchange for sexual favors.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Benja tries to get the money his father owes. Juanma thinks back and remembers a disturbing fact about the party. Rodri agrees to Alma's proposal.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Benja asks Facu to help recover the money that Gaby stole. Ariana's father does something unexpected when convincing her to receive a transplant.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Rodri loses the money he borrowed to save his company. Juanma and Flor make each other jealous. Benja and Ariana agree to wed, but she has a secret.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Three months after Ariana left, Benja has a new girlfriend. Flor and Juanma plan their wedding; Rodri works for his sister. But changes are coming...
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Benja is torn between Ariana and Pau. Full of doubts about marriage, Flor cheats on Juanma. Ariana takes charge of her dad's business and fires Gaby.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Aware of Benja and Pau's plan to take her inheritance, Ariana goes to war with them. Rodri welcomes foreign investors. Flor disappears mysteriously.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Ariana get closer; Gaby and Pau play dirty. Juanma tries to get over Flor's cheating. Rodri tries his luck at the adult video business.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Benja tries to adjust to prison. Two suitors propose to Ariana but she can't and won't choose. Flor tries (unsuccessfully) to make peace with Juanma.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Benja's life is in danger in prison. Gaby wants to ruin Ariana. Juanma and Rodri get an offer to buy the app, but they need Benja to sign on.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Benja finds an unexpected ally. Ariana is overwhelmed by her suitors' jealousy and Rodri is overwhelmed by the sex tape business.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Benja is afraid of never getting out. Ariana surprises her suitor with a daring proposal. Powerful businessman Axel Forte wants to buy "Comoencasa."
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Benja has success as an influencer. Rodri and Juanma enjoy their new lives as millionaires. Ariana fulfills a fantasy, but it isn't what she expected.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Without knowing, Benja gets involved with √Ålvarez's daughter. Juanma and Rodri want to buy the coworking space, but someone beats them to it.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Axel takes over the coworking space and names Julia as his number two. Benja gives Facu, who is being threatened by his father, a place to stay.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Juancho convinces Benja to pursue judgement on Ariana. Juanma and Rodri make a bet and win a share of the coworking space.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Ariana unmask Juancho. Juanma hooks up with Axel's sister. Flor and Alma compete for Ramiro's attention‚Äîuntil they decide to share it.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Benja feels burdened by Natalia, who's moved into the house. Ramiro confesses that he's a virgin, and Alma and Flor want to fix that.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Benja interferes with his dad's girlfriend. Ramiro has a psychotic break, and Flor and Alma are at risk. Axel suggests making up with Rodri and Alma.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Juanma gets threats from the Chinese mob. Natalia's obsession with Benja becomes dangerous for everyone. Alma feels bad about sleeping with Axel.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Ariana give themselves another chance, but Gaby reappears to complicate things. Axel makes an indecent proposal to Rodri and Alma.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Gaby goes to Axel to sow discord between Benja and Ariana. Facu gets involved with Axel's cousin. Flor starts seeing Leo, an old friend of Juanma's.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Gaby takes charge of the coworking space. Benja leaves being an influencer behind to study. Octavio encourages Rodri as a singer.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Gaby manipulates Juanma to meet her goals. Ariana and Alma worry about Flor's toxic relationship with Leo. Rodri is a hit online; Benja is jealous.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Mysteriously, the Comoencasa app begins to lose customers. Benja receives a tempting job offer. Rodri thinks he's a star and contacts an agent.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Benja falls into Gaby's trap again. Flor is abused by Leo; Ariana and Alma come to her defense. Benja and Juanma try to solve the mystery of the app.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Juanma discover that a gang has been using their app to sell drugs. Leo holds Flor captive. Rodri, obsessed with fame, ignores Alma.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Benja, Juanma and Rodri are arrested, and Gaby helps them out. Flor gets the courage to leave Leo. Juanma and Gaby's relationship is in danger.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Benja tells Ariana that he fathered a child years ago. Juanma defends Flor, which gets him in trouble with Gaby. Lauti blackmails Rodri with a video.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Benja begins to look for his son. Rodri starts having panic attacks again. Juanma and Flor become roommates.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Flor and Juanma try out an open relationship. Alma is jealous of Rodri and a well-known influencer. Benja is involved in a police corruption plot.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: The girls decide to spend the night just them, and they suggest the boys do the same. Gaby offers Juanma a plan that will sink Benja.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Benja saves Facu's life. Juanma and Ariana are attracted to one another. Alma represents Rodri. Ariana wants to find out what Gaby is hiding.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Benja finds out that Ariana cheated on him with Juanma and the news makes everyone crazy, especially Flor. Ariana finds out Gaby's big secret.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Benja and Ariana unleash their love. Scorned, Benja teams up with Gaby to take control of everything. A report threatens to end Rodri's career.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: An attack with hostages taken puts everyone in the coworking space at risk. Benja and Juanma put their differences aside to save their loved ones.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: In Mexico, Juanma accepts a racy proposal. Benja receives startling text messages from an anonymous sender. Work comes between Rodri and Alma.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Benja is punished for disbelieving the boy texting him. After failing to win over potential new investors, Axel takes a gamble with Shine Bag's funds.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: To promote Shine Bag, Benja organizes a costume party, where Juanma takes a risk, Clash cheers up Julia, and a jealous outburst takes a sudden turn.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Axel launches an online contest in search of new talent for Shine Bag. Ariana receives some advice from Ramiro. Benja gets to know Lautaro better.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Fran and Julia go out for coffee. Axel asks Ramiro for money. The love triangle between Rodri, Alma and Juanma continues to develop.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Ariana gives a gift to Ramiro, who invites her to his home. Julia tries to find a way to stay close to Fran. Juanma enters the Shine Bag contest.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Ariana confides in her psychologist. Flor, Axel and Gaby visit Indra's ashram. Rodri has a frank talk with Juanma and an explosive encounter with Ariel.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Medical advice leads Ariana to make a decision about Benja. Axel sees the video of Benja performing with Lautaro and tries to find out who the boy is.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Rodri visits the doctor. Juanma discovers Rodri is being blackmailed. Ramiro presents Ariana with the power-of-attorney document to sign.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Ariana discovers her assets have been frozen. Rodri is caught kissing Ariel. The Shine Bag contest winner is crowned.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Ariana meets Benja's son, and is later visited by Juanma. Axel confronts Benja about hacking the contest. Rodri's despair takes him to a dark place.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Flor proposes a spicy new idea to Axel. Ariana tells Benja about Emilio's offer. A hero comes to Vilma's rescue during a robbery.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: A video of Gaby goes viral ‚Äî without her consent. While going for a walk, Alma sees Rodri with Ariel. Juanma finds himself the victim of blackmail.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Juanma is arrested by the police. With Flor's help, Gaby gives Axel a taste of his own medicine. Benja suspects Emilio has romantic feelings for him.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Juanma tries to help the cops catch Shantal. The paternity of Ariana's baby is determined. Rodri separates from Alma to decide who he wants to be with.
episodes.title: Episode 15
